query:
SELECT * FROM (
                SELECT
                    index,
                    init_transaction_index,
                    total_supply as raw_total_supply,
                    token_id,
                    contract_index,
                    contract_sub_index,
                    token_address,
                    metadata_url
                FROM tokens
                WHERE 
                    starts_with(token_address, $5)
                    AND tokens.index > $1 
                    AND tokens.index < $2
                ORDER BY
                    (CASE WHEN $4 THEN tokens.index END) ASC,
                    (CASE WHEN NOT $4 THEN tokens.index END) DESC
                LIMIT $3
            ) AS token_data
            ORDER BY token_data.index ASC
